{"rule_id": "66fca49b-05f8-4895-a2f1-e46615951f01", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "category_qualification", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "SHEIN Marketplace 卖家入驻资质要求", "summary": "SHEIN Marketplace 仅面向合法注册的企业开放，不接受个人/个体卖家，且通常要求较高的年营收门槛与本地化运营能力。", "content": "- 必须为在受支持国家/地区合法注册的企业实体（如美国、英国、欧盟成员国等），不接受个人或个体工商户。\n- 部分地区要求卖家具备较高年营收规模（媒体概括为约 500 万美元/年量级）——**该数值阈值为二手概括，待核验**。\n- 美区新卖家通常需为美国本土企业，并具备本地发货能力。\n- 资质与品类要求按地区（US/EU/UK）及商品类目不同而变化。\n- 申请通过卖家中心提交，审核周期通常为 1–3 个工作日。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://eur.shein.com/tc-overview-a-3172.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["category_qualification", "eligibility", "business_registration", "onboarding"]}
{"rule_id": "20f2199a-17b2-498b-8c35-57c91ee7ce5c", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "prohibited_products", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "禁售与受限商品规则", "summary": "卖家不得上架违反平台条款、适用法律或第三方权利的商品；不合规商品一经发现将被全球下架。", "content": "- 卖家须遵守 SHEIN 平台服务协议及所在销售国的商品安全法律法规。\n- 平台对违禁品采用自动标记 + 人工审核机制进行筛查。\n- 任何在任一司法辖区被认定不符合安全要求的商品，将被**立即全球下架**，并由合规团队进行差距分析、必要时召回并退款。\n- 涉及电子产品、儿童玩具/用品、婴童用品、化妆品、医疗器械、PPE、纺织品等受限类目需先提交合规证明方可上架。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.sheingroup.com/governance", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["prohibited_products", "restricted", "safety", "delisting"]}
{"rule_id": "b66c49ed-4e0f-46ad-92a2-21e01db483f0", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "intellectual_property", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "反假冒与知识产权侵权政策", "summary": "Marketplace 卖家受平台《反假冒与知识产权侵权政策》约束，须承诺商品不侵犯第三方知识产权，否则面临下架与封号。", "content": "- 卖家须遵守平台服务协议中的《反假冒与知识产权侵权政策》，并自证商品不侵犯第三方商标、版权、专利或外观设计权。\n- 专门团队使用图像识别技术 + 人工方式在商品上线前进行扫描审核。\n- 对**反复或严重**侵权的卖家，平台可终止其 Marketplace 访问与使用权限。\n- 平台可就侵权向责任方提起法律程序，按赔偿基础追偿全部成本。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://m.shein.com/copyright-noticeam-a-379.html?lang=en", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["intellectual_property", "anti_counterfeiting", "trademark", "copyright", "patent"]}
{"rule_id": "70ff0aec-3ed6-4b65-9224-267801007e28", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "intellectual_property", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "知识产权投诉与下架处理流程", "summary": "权利人可通过专门的 IP 投诉门户提交侵权通知（商标/版权/专利/外观设计），平台据此发出警告、下架并通知被投诉方。", "content": "- 平台运营专门的 IP 投诉门户，供权利人提交侵权下架通知。\n- 投诉须包含权利人善意声明：被指控的侵权使用未获权利人、其代理或法律授权。\n- 平台处理措施可包括：向被指控方发出警告、移除/禁用侵权材料、通知被指控方、必要时暂停其 Marketplace 访问权限。\n- 被投诉卖家可通过客服渠道对下架/封号决定提出申诉。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://m.shein.com/copyright-noticeam-a-379.html?lang=en", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["intellectual_property", "ip_complaint", "takedown", "appeal"]}
{"rule_id": "aa56b584-e78f-42fb-97d4-b4c3e2812667", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "退货政策（30 天退货窗口）", "summary": "平台提供 30 天退货窗口；商品须未穿着、未洗涤、未损坏并保留原始吊牌与包装。平台代卖家处理退货并发放退款。", "content": "- 退货窗口为 30 天，商品须为未穿/未洗/未损、吊牌完整、尽量保留原包装。\n- 每个订单**首次退货免费**；同一订单后续退货通常扣除约 7.99 美元退货费——**该数值为二手概括，待核验**。\n- 平台代卖家处理退货流程并发放退款（含账户管理、在线收款与退货时的赔付）。\n- 退款可退至原支付方式或 SHEIN 钱包。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://us.shein.com/Return-Policy-a-281.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["returns_refunds", "return_window", "return_fee"]}
{"rule_id": "8a009106-f810-4b34-a2ea-5c102b4fe5f5", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "不可退货商品类目", "summary": "部分类目商品不支持退货，鞋类/配饰/电子产品有更严格的包装要求。", "content": "- 不可退货商品通常包括：内衣、珠宝、化妆品、宠物用品、清仓/最终特卖品、赠品及定制商品。\n- 鞋类、配饰、电子产品适用更严格的退货包装要求。\n- 卖家应在商品信息中准确标注退货属性，避免因退货纠纷影响账户表现。\n- **具体不可退类目以平台最新页面为准，待核验**。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://us.shein.com/Return-Policy-a-281.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["returns_refunds", "non_returnable", "categories"]}
{"rule_id": "0793f11e-feb3-4961-946b-5e391ceca744", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "退款方式与到账时效", "summary": "退款可退至 SHEIN 钱包（通常 24 小时内）或原支付方式（约 1–10 个工作日，视银行而定）。", "content": "- SHEIN 钱包退款通常在处理后 24 小时内到账，可即时用于平台消费，亦可后续提现至银行卡。\n- 原路退款到账时效约 1–10 个工作日，具体取决于银行。\n- **到账时效为二手概括，待核验**。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://us.shein.com/refund-a-1703.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["returns_refunds", "refund", "wallet", "timeline"]}
{"rule_id": "0d1837cb-1175-4986-81dc-945b4c9ffcfb", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "fee", "title": "Marketplace 佣金费率", "summary": "平台一般不收取入驻费或月费，按成交收取佣金；基础费率约 10%，并随地区与类目浮动。", "content": "- 无入驻费、无月费、无强制广告费。\n- 基础佣金约为成交额的 10%；不同地区/类目存在浮动（媒体概括女装高端类目可达约 25%，UK 站约 12.24%）——**费率数值为二手概括，待核验**。\n- 多数新卖家享有前 30 天 0% 佣金的导入期——**该优惠期为二手概括，待核验**。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://eur.shein.com/tc-overview-a-3172.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["fees", "commission", "payout"]}
{"rule_id": "13b3a54c-a105-4327-9ea4-692d6746eb73", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "fee", "title": "Fulfillment by SHEIN 仓储与操作费", "summary": "使用 SHEIN 履约服务（SFS）的卖家需承担按件计的操作与仓储费，以及超期长期仓储费。", "content": "- SFS 操作与仓储费按商品尺寸/重量约 0.30–1.10 美元/件，超 30 天长期仓储约 0.03 美元/天/件——**以上数值为二手概括，待核验**。\n- SFS 采用统一 10% 佣金（非按件费率）。\n- 具体费率以平台 SFS 官方价目为准。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://open.sheincorp.com/documents/system/b86df826-638d-4128-9f5e-c7b20d8cf28e", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["fees", "fulfillment", "sfs", "storage"]}
{"rule_id": "43908a13-aa05-4d70-a1bb-d0387fad7f35", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "penalties", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "penalty", "title": "超时未送达罚则", "summary": "订单未在规定时效（约 7 个工作日）内送达，每单将产生罚款。", "content": "- 订单未在约 7 个工作日内送达，每单将被处以约 1 美元罚款——**该数值为二手概括，待核验**。\n- 履约时效标准（媒体概括）：24 小时内处理、48 小时内发货、5 天内上传物流单号、7 天内送达。\n- 持续的履约超时将影响账户表现与店铺权重。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://open.sheincorp.com/documents/system/b86df826-638d-4128-9f5e-c7b20d8cf28e", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["penalties", "late_delivery", "fulfillment", "sla"]}
{"rule_id": "765284e0-9c94-4e32-9986-abe57dbe7401", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "penalties", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "penalty", "title": "账户暂停与终止规则", "summary": "违反条款、适用法律或第三方权利的内容/行为可导致账户暂停或终止；提供虚假信息或规避平台机制构成重大违约。", "content": "- 任何不符合条款、适用法律或第三方权利的内容（contribution），平台可予以暂停。\n- 试图绕过、操纵或提供虚假信息构成**重大违约**，可导致账户立即暂停或终止。\n- 反复或严重侵犯知识产权的卖家可被终止 Marketplace 访问权限。\n- 卖家可通过联系客服对下架/封禁/暂停决定提出申诉。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://us.shein.com/Terms-and-Conditions-a-399.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["penalties", "suspension", "termination", "material_breach", "appeal"]}
{"rule_id": "59ada4ed-1fef-458f-baa3-15b94702420d", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "penalties", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "penalty", "title": "合规不达标卖家清退", "summary": "平台对不满足合规要求的卖家执行清退；自 Marketplace 上线以来已终止与大量不合规卖家的合作。", "content": "- 平台对不满足产品安全/合规要求的卖家执行终止合作。\n- 媒体概括：自 Marketplace 上线以来已清退 540+ 不合规卖家——**该数值为二手概括，待核验**。\n- 平台治理框架包含资质准入、多层筛查、持续监控与更严格的执法。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.sheingroup.com/newsroom/shein-expands-marketplace-seller-education-offering-with-product-safety-and-quality-compliance", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["penalties", "compliance", "termination", "governance"]}
{"rule_id": "07ffd3f8-8427-44c4-abfa-b874c7c5799a", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "商品图片规范", "summary": "商品图须为高质量 JPG/JPEG/PNG，受文件大小与尺寸限制；视觉质量直接影响审核与转化。", "content": "- 图片格式：JPG/JPEG/PNG，单图通常 < 3 MB。\n- 尺寸要求（媒体概括）：竖图最高约 1340 × 1785 px；方图约 900–2200 px——**尺寸数值为二手概括，待核验**。\n- 因平台高度视觉化，清晰、有造型的图片通常优于普通产品图，对审核通过与转化影响显著。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://eur.shein.com/tc-overview-a-3172.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["listing", "images", "media", "content_quality"]}
{"rule_id": "0e3943ea-28b3-4c97-84d8-31adb6f5b44b", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "商品必填属性与刊登要求", "summary": "刊登须包含尺寸、重量、描述及至少一张图片等必填信息；尽量补全属性可提升曝光与转化。", "content": "- 必填信息至少包含：商品尺寸、重量、描述与至少一张图片。\n- 须填写标题、描述、品牌与货号，并按规格选择颜色、尺码（可自定义）。\n- 部分类目需额外属性（如女装连衣裙类目的 Style Features）及主规格图。\n- 属性映射越完整，商品曝光与转化通常越高。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://eur.shein.com/tc-overview-a-3172.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["listing", "attributes", "required_fields", "catalog"]}
{"rule_id": "d76970b8-bf66-4a62-bf20-02c7b8208cab", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "SHEIN 履约服务（SFS）运作方式", "summary": "卖家可批量将货物送至 SFS 仓，由平台完成入库质检、仓储、拣货、打包与配送，并提供实时库存追踪。", "content": "- 卖家批量备货至 SFS 仓，到仓后由平台进行质检与入库存储。\n- 卖家可通过平台系统实时查看库存。\n- 订单产生后由平台拣货、打包、配送，统一符合平台包装与质量标准。\n- SFS 为邀请制，通常面向较大规模卖家——**准入门槛为二手概括，待核验**。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://open.sheincorp.com/documents/system/b86df826-638d-4128-9f5e-c7b20d8cf28e", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["logistics_fulfillment", "sfs", "warehouse", "inventory"]}
{"rule_id": "400f48a3-f0e7-4f76-bb5f-8c30f8d68e3f", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "自发货履约时效标准", "summary": "自发货卖家须在规定时效内处理、发货、上传单号并送达，否则触发超时罚则。", "content": "- 履约时效（媒体概括）：24 小时内处理订单、48 小时内发货、5 天内上传物流单号、7 天内送达。\n- 未达 7 天送达标准每单罚款约 1 美元。\n- **以上时效与罚款数值为二手概括，待核验**。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://open.sheincorp.com/documents/system/b86df826-638d-4128-9f5e-c7b20d8cf28e", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["logistics_fulfillment", "sla", "shipping", "tracking"]}
{"rule_id": "e0e89547-02ba-4ac6-97dd-5393d735afe8", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "账户健康与持续合规监控", "summary": "平台通过资质准入、多层筛查与持续监控维护卖家账户健康；履约、退货及合规表现影响店铺权重与权限。", "content": "- 治理框架含资质准入、多层筛查与持续监控。\n- 履约超时、高退货率、合规缺陷等会影响账户表现与曝光权重，严重者面临限制或清退。\n- 卖家须按类目要求完成合规培训并通过课程考核，部分类目需定期再认证。\n- **具体量化考核阈值未在公开来源给出，待核验**。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.sheingroup.com/newsroom/shein-expands-marketplace-seller-education-offering-with-product-safety-and-quality-compliance", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["account_health", "monitoring", "performance", "recertification"]}
{"rule_id": "027df387-fb8a-4de0-bd88-7e67da20bb29", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "促销与折扣展示规则", "summary": "平台设有促销规则页面，规范折扣/参考价的使用与展示；不得使用虚假参考价或误导性折扣。", "content": "- 平台《Promotion Rules》页面规范促销活动的展示与折扣口径。\n- 参考价/原价须真实，禁止以虚高原价制造虚假折扣（多地监管已就此对平台执法）。\n- 卖家应避免虚假倒计时、低库存提示等\"暗黑模式\"诱导手段。\n- **具体折扣展示细则以促销规则页最新内容为准，待核验**。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://us.shein.com/promotion-rules-a-737.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["advertising", "promotion", "discount", "reference_price", "dark_patterns"]}
{"rule_id": "36e8ea8f-9a3a-4192-91e9-dcd96d85d6ef", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "营销内容真实性要求", "summary": "卖家营销内容须真实准确，纳入平台合规培训范围，涵盖商品属性与宣传口径。", "content": "- 平台合规培训涵盖\"营销内容准确性\"，要求商品属性提交准确、宣传不夸大、不误导。\n- 环境/可持续等宣称须有事实依据，避免\"漂绿\"。\n- 不实宣传可触发下架与合规处置。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.sheingroup.com/newsroom/shein-expands-marketplace-seller-education-offering-with-product-safety-and-quality-compliance", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["advertising", "marketing", "accuracy", "greenwashing"]}
{"rule_id": "5d8af6ae-8367-4817-af83-93bb9022e2ed", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "tax_compliance", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "EU GPSR 合规与责任人要求", "summary": "在欧盟销售的非食品商品须有位于欧盟的\"责任人\"（Responsible Person），承担安全相关合规职责。", "content": "- 欧盟《通用产品安全条例》(GPSR) 自 2024-12-13 起生效，要求每件非食品商品在欧盟有一名\"责任人\"。\n- 责任人作为面向监管机构的联系点，确保商品符合适用安全要求并具备制造商联系信息。\n- 非欧盟制造商通常需指定欧盟责任人/授权代表。\n- **此为通用监管要求概括，平台具体落地细则待核验**。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.sheingroup.com/governance", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["tax_compliance", "gpsr", "responsible_person", "eu", "product_safety"]}
{"rule_id": "5e51cf30-dd38-4e9b-94f7-e48cfb63ee2a", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "tax_compliance", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "EU 生产者责任延伸（EPR）合规", "summary": "在欧盟投放包装商品的卖家通常须按国家注册 EPR、加入生产者责任组织并申报包装量、缴纳 EPR 费用。", "content": "- EPR 使包装\"生产者\"对包装废弃物的收集、分类与回收承担财务责任。\n- 实践中卖家须在投放市场的每个国家注册、加入 PRO、申报包装量并缴费。\n- **此为通用监管要求概括，平台具体落地细则待核验**。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.sheingroup.com/governance", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["tax_compliance", "epr", "packaging", "eu"]}
{"rule_id": "19b3b433-e758-4726-9ba9-6764354a36f9", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "tax_compliance", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "增值税与海关申报义务", "summary": "从非欧盟发货的卖家与平台须向海关提供必要数据、缴纳或担保税费，并确保商品符合欧盟法规。", "content": "- 跨境销售需向海关提供必要数据，缴纳或担保相关税费。\n- 进口与税务义务通常落在进口商、增值税注册卖家或申报伙伴身上。\n- **此为通用监管要求概括，平台具体落地细则待核验**。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.sheingroup.com/governance", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["tax_compliance", "vat", "customs", "import"]}
{"rule_id": "9fcd7dfa-d4fa-4732-ab00-76d55500b2f8", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "payments", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "卖家回款与结算周期", "summary": "卖家货款通常按周期（如 Net-14/Net-30 或每周）通过银行转账结算，待退货窗口与签收确认后释放。", "content": "- 回款一般通过银行转账或支持的收款方式发放，常见为每周结算。\n- 结算周期（媒体概括）通常为 Net-14 或 Net-30，视卖家层级与地区而定。\n- 货款在客户退货窗口结束且物流确认送达后释放。\n- **结算周期数值为二手概括，待核验**。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://eur.shein.com/tc-overview-a-3172.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["payments", "payout", "settlement", "net_terms"]}
{"rule_id": "ed981ca6-89e2-457e-9c6f-00f4cd549e57", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "payments", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "收款账户信息维护", "summary": "卖家可在后台维护财务信息，新增或修改用于接收平台回款的银行账户。", "content": "- 平台支持卖家在后台更新财务信息。\n- 卖家可添加或修改用于接收平台回款的银行账户。\n- **具体支持的收款方式与限制以后台为准，待核验**。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://eur.shein.com/tc-overview-a-3172.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["payments", "bank_account", "seller_center"]}
{"rule_id": "2919e1b4-f8d6-4d0b-9904-ec88466c530c", "platform": "shein", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "平台代卖家处理售后与退款", "summary": "平台代卖家处理退货流程并代为发放退款，涵盖账户管理、在线收款与退货赔付。", "content": "- 平台代卖家管理退货流程、在线收款处理与退货时的赔付/退款。\n- 卖家售后责任与平台代办边界以服务协议为准。\n- 退货费、运单扣费、平台罚则等会影响卖家最终结算金额。\n- **具体扣费项目与边界待核验**。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://us.shein.com/Return-Policy-a-281.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["after_sales", "returns_handling", "refund", "settlement"]}
{"rule_id": "f65e20d4-4faf-4519-9397-5cab9486f8cc", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "prohibited_products", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "受限物质清单（RSL/MRSL）合规", "summary": "卖家须遵守平台《受限物质清单》(RSL) 与《制造受限物质清单》(MRSL)，皮肤接触类商品须通过化学安全检测。", "content": "- 卖家（含制造伙伴与第三方卖家）须遵守适用商品安全法规及平台 RSL、供应商行为准则等管控标准。\n- 皮肤接触类商品须满足化学限量并通过检测。\n- 电子、儿童玩具/用品、婴童、化妆品、医疗器械、PPE、纺织品等类目须提交证书与检测报告方可上架。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.sheingroup.com/governance", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["prohibited_products", "rsl", "mrsl", "chemical_safety", "testing"]}
{"rule_id": "8614ff61-894e-49e4-9e63-02009ba6cb08", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "category_qualification", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "受限类目合规文件准入", "summary": "电子、儿童用品、化妆品、医疗器械等受限类目须先提交证书与检测报告，通过系统校验与人工审核后方可刊登。", "content": "- 受限类目（电子、儿童玩具/用品、婴童、化妆品、医疗器械、轻工、PPE、纺织品等）须先提交合规文件。\n- 提交内容含证书与检测报告，经平台系统校验 + 人工审核。\n- 高压电子类商品须核验如欧盟 RoHS、美国 FCC 等认证。\n- 未通过合规文件审核的商品不得上架。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.sheingroup.com/newsroom/shein-further-intensifies-product-safety-and-quality-protocols-targets-2-5-million-tests-in-2025", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["category_qualification", "compliance_docs", "certification", "rohs", "fcc"]}
{"rule_id": "386067e1-e381-416f-8df7-6fa129f559f4", "platform": "shein", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "卖家合规培训与认证义务", "summary": "卖家须通过卖家教育中心完成结构化合规培训并通过考核，部分类目需定期再认证。", "content": "- 卖家教育中心提供按市场/类目的合规指引与上百门合规课程（短视频、直播、互动模块 + 考核）。\n- 培训覆盖商品安全文档、商品属性准确提交、受限物质合规与营销内容准确性。\n- 卖家须完成培训模块、提交达标文档，许多类目需通过周期性再认证。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.sheingroup.com/newsroom/shein-expands-marketplace-seller-education-offering-with-product-safety-and-quality-compliance", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["account_health", "training", "education_hub", "recertification"]}
